		{
			dependencies: ["3903C286AAE568C9"]
			description: [
				"After you have scienced enough &bAxolotls&r, you'll be able to do some more interesting things, like create spawn eggs."
				""
				"Remember how way back in Chapter 1, you built a &9worm farm&r? But it wasn't a true farm, in the sense of producing &9worms&r on its own, without your manual intervention. Now you can fix that!"
				""
				"&aSugar Gliders&r are really good at foraging for insects when they are placed upon a &9leaf block&r. Now, maybe you haven't found a Sugar Glider yet. Not to worry. Make yourself some &9stem cells&r, pour some &1liquid science&r on it, and you've got an &9embryo&r ready to be made into a &9Sugar Glider Spawn Egg&r."
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "kubejs:embryo"
