		{
			dependencies: ["1266905BED12A811"]
			description: ["Now, it's just matter of setting up a breeding chamber for your &aAxolotls&r, and feeding the offspring into the &9Sciencery&r. I'm sure that with a clever use of &9leads&r, &9fans&r and &aRats&r you can keep science running even when you're not around."]
