		}
		{
			dependencies: ["3FA3C3C16A9DF41B"]
			description: [
				"Ok, so maybe the &aSugar Glider&r doesn't find &9worms&r all that quickly. Not to worry! There is another way."
				""
				"You've already automated the creation of the &9meatwad&r. With those, you can construct &9breeding chow&r, which is useful for breeding most meat-eaters, including &aAxolotls&r. Just set up your &aRats&r to craft it and give it to your axolotls, and you're in business."
			]
			id: "6079EDB456F3DE89"
			rewards: [{
				count: 5
