		{
			dependencies: ["592C13B11CD5EC9A"]
			description: [
				"To generate our anecdotes we will need another animal to experiment on. Three are suitable. &aRats&r are viable, but will also be the least productive. Next are &aRabbits&r, a classic lab animal. But the best of all are &aGuinea Pigs&r. If you have not yet encountered any in your travels, you now have the technology to create their spawn egg in the lab, and should do so."
				""
				"As with your &aAxolotls&r, you will want to set some aside for breeding, while sending the rest into the &9Sciencery&r. "
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "kubejs:anecdotes_bucket"
				tag: { }
			}
			id: "0B3C743441943C29"
			subtitle: "The singular of data"
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "6813382765EF59A8"
					item: {
						Count: 1
