		}
		{
			dependencies: ["01B494C61A52BB02"]
			description: ["Sorry, it turns out that Reviewer 2 didn't like your paper. We're going to need to punch it up a bit. Let's turn to that other great source of science: &1anecdotes&r. Enough of them is basically the same thing as data, right?"]
