		{
			dependencies: ["3FA3C3C16A9DF41B"]
			description: ["You can use the &9embryo&r to construct all manner of &9spawn eggs&r. Take a look through the recipe book for some that might be useful. This is much easier than running around the world trying to find them in the wild."]
