		{
			dependencies: ["41F5F15BE95C79DC"]
			description: [
				"Our research is almost complete. Take everything you've made so far: the &1experimental results&r, the &1anecdotes&r, the &1citations&r, and mix them together inside a &9Sciencery&r. Behold, &1liquid science&r! Pour that out into a &9casting basin&r and you have yourself &9hard science&r."
				""
				"With that, you are ready for &2Chapter 4&r. It's time to bring back the dinosaurs."
