		{
			dependencies: ["0B3C743441943C29"]
			description: [
				"A new technology has been unlocked!"
				""
				"You can greatly shrink most of your animal farms now. Harden those &1anecdotes&r into &9wisdom&r, and construct a &9mob cage&r. Put an appropriate block in the cage so that it will be a good environment for your animal."
				""
				"Next, make a &9DNA Sampler&r. Stick the animal you want to replicate, then deposit the sample in the cage. From then on, science will automatically harvest the drops for you. &9DNA Samplers&r are one-time use."
				""
				"Higher tier samplers can be used on hostile mobs, or even bosses."
			]
